'''深度学习超级采样'''（Deep Learning Super Sampling，DLSS）是[[英伟达|Nvidia]]开发的一种[[图像缩放|图像缩放]]技术，可实时用于[[视频游戏|视频游戏]]中，這種技術利用[[深度学习|深度学习]]将较低[[解析度|解析度]]的图像[[图像缩放|缩放]]為更高[[解析度|解析度]]的图像，以便在更高[[解析度|解析度]]的计算机[[显示器|显示器]]上显示<ref>{{Cite web|title=Nvidia RTX DLSS: Everything you need to know|url=https://www.digitaltrends.com/computing/everything-you-need-to-know-about-nvidias-rtx-dlss-technology/|accessdate=2020-04-05|date=2020-02-14|publisher=[[Digital_Trends|Digital Trends]]|quote=''Deep learning super sampling uses artificial intelligence and machine learning to produce an image that looks like a higher-resolution image, without the rendering overhead. Nvidia’s algorithm learns from tens of thousands of rendered sequences of images that were created using a supercomputer. That trains the algorithm to be able to produce similarly beautiful images, but without requiring the graphics card to work as hard to do it.''|archive-date=2018-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181102131151/https://www.digitaltrends.com/computing/everything-you-need-to-know-about-nvidias-rtx-dlss-technology/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 历史 ==
Nvidia在2018年9月推出[[NVIDIA_GeForce_20系列|NVIDIA GeForce 20系列]][[GPU|GPU]]时，將DLSS作為賣點進行宣傳<ref name="techspot">{{Cite web|title=Nvidia DLSS in 2020: stunning results|url=https://www.techspot.com/article/1992-nvidia-dlss-2020/|accessdate=2020-04-05|date=2020-02-26|publisher=techspot.com|archive-date=2020-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200228070336/https://www.techspot.com/article/1992-nvidia-dlss-2020/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。当时，DLSS的效果仅限于少数几款视频游戏（如《[[战地5|战地5]]》和《[[戰慄深隧：流亡|戰慄深隧：流亡]]》） <ref>{{Cite web|title=AMD Thinks NVIDIA DLSS is not Good Enough; Calls TAA & SMAA Better Alternatives|url=https://www.techquila.co.in/nvidia-dlss-vs-taa/|accessdate=2020-04-06|date=2019-02-15|publisher=techquila.co.in|quote=''Recently, two big titles received NVIDIA DLSS support, namely Metro Exodus and Battlefield V. Both these games come with NVIDIA’s DXR (DirectX Raytracing) implentation that at the moment is only supported by the GeForce RTX cards. DLSS makes these games playable at higher resolutions with much better frame rates, although there is a notable decrease in image sharpness. Now, AMD has taken a jab at DLSS, saying that traditional AA methods like SMAA and TAA “offer superior combinations of image quality and performance.”''|archive-date=2019-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190215191416/https://www.techquila.co.in/nvidia-dlss-vs-taa/|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref name="kotaku">{{Cite web|title=Nvidia Very Quietly Made DLSS A Hell Of A Lot Better|url=https://www.kotaku.com.au/2020/02/nvidia-rtx-dlss-quietly-got-a-hell-of-a-lot-better/|accessdate=2020-04-06|date=2020-02-22|publisher=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]|quote=''The benefit for most people is that, generally, DLSS comes with a sizeable FPS improvement. How much varies from game to game. In Metro Exodus, the FPS jump was barely there and certainly not worth the bizarre hit to image quality.''|archive-date=2020-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200929163554/https://www.kotaku.com.au/2020/02/nvidia-rtx-dlss-quietly-got-a-hell-of-a-lot-better/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 2020年4月，Nvidia推出DLSS 2.0，该版本的DLSS适用于《[[控制_(遊戲)|控制]]》和《[[德軍總部：新血脈|德軍總部：新血脈]]》等游戏<ref name="techspot" /> <ref name="gamersnexus">{{Cite web|title=HW News - Crysis Remastered Ray Tracing, NVIDIA DLSS 2, Ryzen 3100 Rumors|url=https://www.gamersnexus.net/news-pc/3572-hw-news-crysis-remastered-ray-tracing-on-amd-nvidia|accessdate=2020-04-19|date=2020-04-19|quote=''“The original DLSS required training the AI network for each new game. DLSS 2.0 trains using non-game-specific content, delivering a generalized network that works across games. This means faster game integrations, and ultimately more DLSS games.”''|archive-date=2020-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926224142/https://www.gamersnexus.net/news-pc/3572-hw-news-crysis-remastered-ray-tracing-on-amd-nvidia|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

